name: Alphabet Fall.IO - Match Race
description:
Get ready for new Survival io game: Alphabet Fall.IO - Match Race



Let's run around the io arena, pick the right tile to stay on, and don't fall! Play Alphabet Lore Match Party, have a great time, and be the last one standing

In Alphabet Fall.IO - Match Race, your mission is to stay alive in arena full of enemies. The rules are super simple to learn: Guess the right tile, run fast there and push other players out of the arena!



HOW TO PLAY
- Drag to move around arena
- Choose right tile as the picture host show
- Push others out of the land



GAME FEATURE
- Lots of addicting levels
- Fun io gameplay
- Casual brain teaser
- Famous characters
- Simple controls
- Stunning graphics
- Unique player skins



To survive and escape from toy factory, you must be smart, fast, and furious.


Don't wait, DOWNLOAD NOW
